        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I spend my day jumping between a dozen different web apps. Gmail for one client, Slack for another, three different social media dashboards, and two separate project management boards. My browser was a chaotic mess of tabs, and logging in and out was wasting precious minutes. That’s when I found ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "WebCatalog",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", and it completely rewired my workflow.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://try.webcatalog.io/h8kuam5b12qt"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This tool doesn't just create shortcuts; it transforms any website into a standalone desktop application. It feels like magic. Suddenly, my web apps live on my taskbar or dock like native programs. I can manage multiple accounts for the same service side-by-side without needing to open different browsers or use incognito modes. If you're looking for a real productivity upgrade, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "give WebCatalog a try",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
