          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and download the version for your operating system (Mac, Windows, or Linux). The installation is standard—just follow the prompts. Once installed, launch the application. You’ll be greeted by a clean, intuitive interface.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Add Your First Web App",
