        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, WebCatalog offers a generous free tier that allows you to create and manage a limited number of applications. This is perfect for personal use or trying out the core features. For users needing unlimited apps, advanced workspace features, and premium support, there is a paid subscription plan.",
            "marks": []
