        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. While WebCatalog has a curated catalog of pre-configured profiles for popular sites (which ensure optimal performance), you can add *any* website URL to create a custom application for it. The tool simply packages the web page into a standalone app window.",
            "marks": []
          }
